%spark
// URL searching
import scala.math.pow
import java.lang.System.nanoTime
sqlContext.clearCache() // clear memory cache
val t0: Long = nanoTime
//Benchmark: loading and searching 1 url from the file
val df = spark.read.format("parquet").load("D:/spookyHash.parquet.gzip")
val filtered = df.filter($"originalUrl" === "http://redriverradio.org/post/when-cinnamon-spice-not-so-nice-great-danish-debate") 
val t1: Long = nanoTime
val timecost = (t1 - t0).toDouble / pow(10, 9)
println("Total Time (seconds):"+timecost.toString)
